    "temperatureGrade": "-40..150",
    "description": "150 V, 6 mOhm (max) enhancement-mode eGaN power FET in a thermally enhanced 3 x 5 mm QFN with exposed top. Gallium-nitride lateral device with a majority-carrier reverse-conduction path: it has no intrinsic body diode (zero reverse-recovery charge) and reverse conduction is gate-voltage dependent. Values transcribed from the EPC2308 datasheet, revised April 29, 2026."
  },
