  "notes": [
    "EPC2308: 150 V, 6 mOhm (max) enhancement-mode eGaN power FET in a 3 x 5 mm thermally enhanced QFN with exposed top. Values transcribed from the EPC2308 datasheet (revised April 29, 2026): static and maximum-ratings and thermal tables on page 1, dynamic characteristics on page 2, pin configuration (Figure 14) on page 5.",
    "GaN reverse conduction: this device has no intrinsic body diode. diode_forward_voltage (VSD) is the third-quadrant channel-conduction voltage and is gate-voltage dependent, carried here with its V_GS condition; reverse_recovery_charge is zero.",
    "All values normalized to base SI: mOhm to ohm, mA/uA to A, pF to F, nC to C. Parameters marked '#' in the datasheet are defined by design and not production tested (noted in conditionsVerbatim). Pin 2 is the source Kelvin / gate-driver return (function KS); the exposed top of the FET is connected to source."
  ]
